    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4591284>
    dc:description "FIGURE 52. Notodelphyopsis falcifera Schellenberg, 1922, female.A, paragnath; B, maxilla; C, leg 1; D, leg 2; E, leg 4; F, leg 5. Scale bars: A, B, 0.02 mm; C–E, 0.05 mm; F, 0.01 mm." ;
